{"entries":[{"id":"tsk-gen-21-8","title":"Genesis 21:8","author":"R. A. Torrey (editor)","reference":{"book":"GEN","chapterStart":21,"verseStart":8,"chapterEnd":21,"verseEnd":8},"content":"<p>Sarah. 11:29,30; 17:15-19; 18:10-14; 21:1-7; Ro 4:19 unto. 21:10; 25:5</p>"},{"id":"tsk-gen-21-13","title":"Genesis 21:13","author":"R. A. Torrey (editor)","reference":{"book":"GEN","chapterStart":21,"verseStart":13,"chapterEnd":21,"verseEnd":13},"content":"<p>O Lord. 12-14; Ac 10:7,8,22 prosper. 12,31; 39:3; Ezr 8:21; Ne 1:11; Ps 37:5; 90:17; Ro 1:10</p>"},{"id":"tsk-gen-21-18","title":"Genesis 21:18","author":"R. A. Torrey (editor)","reference":{"book":"GEN","chapterStart":21,"verseStart":18,"chapterEnd":21,"verseEnd":18},"content":"<p>bowed. 26,27,52 led me. 27; 22:23; Ex 18:20; Ezr 8:21; Ps 32:8; 48:14; 107:7; Pr 3:5,6; 4:11 Isa 48:17</p>"},{"id":"tsk-gen-21-23","title":"Genesis 21:23","author":"R. A. Torrey (editor)","reference":{"book":"GEN","chapterStart":21,"verseStart":23,"chapterEnd":21,"verseEnd":23},"content":"<p>Send me. 56,59; 28:5,6; 45:24; 2Sa 18:19,27,28; Pr 22:29; Ec 7:10; Lu 8:38,39</p>"},{"id":"tsk-gen-21-28","title":"Genesis 21:28","author":"R. A. Torrey (editor)","reference":{"book":"GEN","chapterStart":21,"verseStart":28,"chapterEnd":21,"verseEnd":28},"content":"<p>they. 1:28; 9:1; 14:19; 17:16; 28:3; 48:15,16,20; Ru 4:11,12 be thou the mother.Or, \"be thou for thousands of myriads;\" a large family being always considered, in ancient times, as a proof of the peculiar blessing and favour of God.</p>\n<p>thousands. Da 7:10 thy seed. 22:17; Le 25:46; De 21:19</p>"},{"id":"tsk-gen-21-33","title":"Genesis 21:33","author":"R. A. Torrey (editor)","reference":{"book":"GEN","chapterStart":21,"verseStart":33,"chapterEnd":21,"verseEnd":33},"content":"<p>Mr 6:30</p>"}]}